Flavor: The Milk Chocolate Flonq Max is the perfected article. This is the chocolate vape that you did not know you needed. Velvety, rich, and sweet, the creamy and milky finish makes this a beverage and a dessert vape. It breaks free from the fruit-ice fusion formula and delivers an unbelievably delicious vaping experience that does not tire the tastebuds.
The refreshing Pink Lemonade Flonq Max has a very realistic lemon flavor paired with a sugary beverage base. A cool and icy finish rounds out this classic salt nic juice flavor.

The Grape Flonq Max oozes sweet grape flavor. Imagine the most delightful grape confection with the refreshing elements of purple Concord grape. It is a bright and sweet flavor, bold enough to never bore the tastebuds thanks to a kick of menthol ice.

Product: Triple Berry Ice Lost Mary MO5000
Flavor: The Triple Berry Ice Lost Mary MO5000 vape contains a sweet, ripened berry blend that has notes of raspberry, blackberry and blueberry flavors and a cool, icy finish.

The Tobacco Flonq Max is an ideal alternative for anyone who prefers authentic tobacco flavors. The combination of the classy Flonq Max appearance, no garish pastel colors here, and a realistic tobacco flavor, this is a perfect choice for adult vapers who use gas station pod kits and have never enjoyed the superior performance of disposable vapes. It is a mild to medium tobacco inspired vape.
